        "name": "Blistering Invective",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "A heap of insults and invectives spew from your mouth\u2014words so devastating your foes burn from the intensity of your diatribe. Your words deal 2d6 persistent fire damage, and the target must attempt a Will save. If the target doesn't understand the language or you're not speaking a language, it gains a +4 circumstance bonus to its save.",
